author: Kyle Newport, Bleacher Report
title: VIDEO: Peewee football players prefer to 'Whip' and 'Nae Nae' over playing football
text: VIDEO: Peewee football players prefer to 'Whip' and 'Nae Nae' over playing football Comment By Kyle Newport, Bleacher Report   Kyle Newport, Bleacher Report  51 AM By Kyle Newport, Bleacher Report  51 AM When your jam comes on, it really doesn't matter where you are or what you are doing. You just have to dance. Instead of focusing on the play before the snap, these youth football players couldn't help but dance when Silento's "Watch Me (Whip/Nae Nae)" came blasting out of the speakers. Essentially, it was a dance party down on the field. Perhaps this is why college and professional stadiums don't play music during plays. By Kyle Newport, Bleacher Report   Kyle Newport, Bleacher Report  51 AM
